# Summer Camp Sports Enrollment System

This is a full-stack web application that allows students to enroll in sports programs offered by a summer camp.

The project was built as part of an internship assignment to demonstrate backend API development, database integration, and frontend interaction.

---

## ðŸš€ Features

- View available sports
- Enroll a student into a selected sport
- Automatically manage available slots
- REST API with interactive Swagger documentation

